    },
    {
      "id": "FloaromaMeadow_Text_ItsAWorksKeyItMustBeForTheValleyWindworks",
      "en_US": [
        "Oh, what’s this thing?\n",
        "They seem to have forgotten it...\r",
        "It’s a Works Key...\n",
        "It must be for the Valley Windworks!\r",
        "It’s of no use to me.\n",
        "You may as well have it.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "FloaromaMeadow_Text_INeedToThankYouThisSweetSweetHoneyGoOnTakeAWholeLot",
      "en_US": [
        "Thank you!\n",
        "You surely saved me.\r",
        "I’d love to repay you, but I don’t\n",
        "have anything of use for you.\r",
        "If you want to find Pokemon\n",
        "attracted to honey, just\f",
        "interact with some honey trees.\r"
      ]
    },
